			input/output error when wiping Intel G2 and OCZ 
			drives with wiper.sh.  Refer to 
			/apps/hdparm/share/doc/wiper/README.txt for more 
			details.
			bash.tcz, gawk.tcz,and possibly others are optional
			dependencies for wiper.sh.
